        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A creature that you can see targets you with an attack.</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You aren't encumbered. With a reflexive burst from your siphons, you try to flit away from the attack. You gain a +2 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack. If the attack fails or critically fails, you can also Stride or Swim up to 10 feet as part of the reaction.</p><hr /><p><strong>Special</strong> If you have the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.feats.Item.Spray Ink] feat, you can also expel a puff of ink as part of this reaction. In addition to the circumstance bonus to AC, you're @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Concealed] against the triggering attack.</p>"
        },
